QuestData.Title: Kinelory Strikes
QuestData.Description: All right, $n. I'm ready if you are.$B$BShall we?
QuestData.LogDescription: Protect Kinelory until she returns to Quae.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Quae in Arathi Highlands.
QuestData.RewardText: You've done a great service for us, $n. Thank you.$B$BI hope Kin wasn't too much of a handful down there. She's very friendly, but can be just as deadly when you're her enemy.
